{
  "verses": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "text": [
        "Your Word Is a Lamp to My Feet"
      ]
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Blessed are those whose way is blameless, who walk in the Law of the LORD."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "2",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Blessed are those who keep His testimonies and seek Him with all their heart."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "3",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "They do no iniquity; they walk in His ways."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "4",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "You have ordained Your precepts, that we should keep them diligently."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "5",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Oh, that my ways were committedto keeping Your statutes!"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "6",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Then I would not be ashamedwhen I consider all Your commandments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "7",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I will praise You with an upright heartwhen I learn Your righteous judgments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "8",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I will keep Your statutes; do not utterly forsake me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "9",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "How can a young man keep his way pure? By guarding it according to Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "10",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "With all my heart I have sought You; do not let me stray from Your commandments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "11",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I have hidden Your word in my heartthat I might not sin against You."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "12",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Blessed are You, O LORD; teach me Your statutes."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "13",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "With my lips I proclaimall the judgments of Your mouth."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "14",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I rejoice in the way of Your testimoniesas much as in all riches."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "15",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I will meditate on Your precepts and regard Your ways."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "16",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I will delight in Your statutes; I will not forget Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "17",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Deal bountifully with Your servant, that I may live and keep Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "18",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Open my eyes that I may seewondrous things from Your law."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "19",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I am a stranger on the earth; do not hide Your commandments from me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "20",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "My soul is consumed with longingfor Your judgments at all times."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "21",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "You rebuke the arrogant—the cursed who stray from Your commandments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "22",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Remove my scorn and contempt, for I have kept Your testimonies."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "23",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Though rulers sit and slander me, Your servant meditates on Your statutes."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "24",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Your testimonies are indeed my delight; they are my counselors."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "25",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "My soul cleaves to the dust; revive me according to Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "26",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I recounted my ways, and You answered me; teach me Your statutes."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "27",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Make clear to me the way of Your precepts; then I will meditate on Your wonders."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "28",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "My soul melts with sorrow; strengthen me according to Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "29",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Remove me from the path of deceit and graciously grant me Your law."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "30",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I have chosen the way of truth; I have set Your ordinances before me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "31",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I cling to Your testimonies, O LORD; let me not be put to shame."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "32",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I run in the path of Your commandments, for You will enlarge my heart."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "33",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Teach me, O LORD, the way of Your statutes, and I will keep them to the end."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "34",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Give me understanding that I may obey Your law, and follow it with all my heart."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "35",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Direct me in the path of Your commandments, for there I find delight."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "36",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Turn my heart to Your testimonies and not to covetous gain."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "37",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Turn my eyes away from worthless things; revive me with Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "38",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Establish Your word to Your servant, to produce reverence for You."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "39",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Turn away the disgrace I dread, for Your judgments are good."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "40",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "How I long for Your precepts! Revive me in Your righteousness."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "41",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "May Your loving devotion come to me, O LORD, Your salvation, according to Your promise."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "42",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Then I can answer him who taunts, for I trust in Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "43",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Never take Your word of truth from my mouth, for I hope in Your judgments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "44",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I will always obey Your law, forever and ever."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "45",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "And I will walk in freedom, for I have sought Your precepts."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "46",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I will speak of Your testimonies before kings, and I will not be ashamed."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "47",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I delight in Your commandmentsbecause I love them."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "48",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I lift up my hands to Your commandments, which I love, and I meditate on Your statutes."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "49",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Remember Your word to Your servant, upon which You have given me hope."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "50",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "This is my comfort in affliction, that Your promise has given me life."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "51",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The arrogant utterly deride me, but I do not turn from Your law."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "52",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I remember Your judgments of old, O LORD, and in them I find comfort."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "53",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Rage has taken hold of mebecause of the wicked who reject Your law."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "54",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Your statutes are songs to mein the house of my pilgrimage."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "55",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "In the night, O LORD, I remember Your name, that I may keep Your law."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "56",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "This is my practice, for I obey Your precepts."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "57",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The LORD is my portion; I have promised to keep Your words."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "58",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I have sought Your face with all my heart; be gracious to me according to Your promise."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "59",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I considered my ways and turned my steps to Your testimonies."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "60",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I hurried without hesitatingto keep Your commandments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "61",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Though the ropes of the wicked bind me, I do not forget Your law."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "62",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "At midnight I rise to give You thanksfor Your righteous judgments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "63",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I am a friend to all who fear You, and to those who keep Your precepts."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "64",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The earth is filled with Your loving devotion, O LORD; teach me Your statutes."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "65",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "You are good to Your servant, O LORD, according to Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "66",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Teach me good judgment and knowledge, for I believe in Your commandments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "67",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Before I was afflicted, I went astray; but now I keep Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "68",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "You are good, and You do what is good; teach me Your statutes."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "69",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Though the arrogant have smeared me with lies, I keep Your precepts with all my heart."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "70",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Their hearts are hard and callous, but I delight in Your law."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "71",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "It was good for me to be afflicted, that I might learn Your statutes."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "72",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The law from Your mouth is more precious to methan thousands of pieces of gold and silver."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "73",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Your hands have made me and fashioned me; give me understanding to learn Your commandments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "74",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "May those who fear You see me and rejoice, for I have hoped in Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "75",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I know, O LORD, that Your judgments are righteous, and that in faithfulness You have afflicted me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "76",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "May Your loving devotion comfort me, I pray, according to Your promise to Your servant."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "77",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "May Your compassion come to me, that I may live, for Your law is my delight."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "78",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "May the arrogant be put to shame for subverting me with a lie; I will meditate on Your precepts."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "79",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "May those who fear You turn to me, those who know Your testimonies."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "80",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "May my heart be blameless in Your statutes, that I may not be put to shame."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "81",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "My soul faints for Your salvation; I wait for Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "82",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "My eyes fail, looking for Your promise; I ask,"
        },
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "When will You comfort me?",
          "speaker": "Unknown"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "83",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Though I am like a wineskin dried up by smoke, I do not forget Your statutes."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "84",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "How many days must Your servant wait? When will You execute judgment on my persecutors?"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "85",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The arrogant have dug pits for mein violation of Your law."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "86",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "All Your commandments are faithful; I am persecuted without cause—help me!"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "87",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "They almost wiped me from the earth, but I have not forsaken Your precepts."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "88",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Revive me according to Your loving devotion, that I may obey the testimony of Your mouth."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "89",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Your word, O LORD, is everlasting; it is firmly fixed in the heavens."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "90",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Your faithfulness continues through all generations; You established the earth, and it endures."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "91",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Your ordinances st and to this day, for all things are servants to You."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "92",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "If Your law had not been my delight, then I would have perished in my affliction."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "93",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I will never forget Your precepts, for by them You have revived me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "94",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I am Yours; save me, for I have sought Your precepts."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "95",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The wicked wait to destroy me, but I will ponder Your testimonies."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "96",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I have seen a limit to all perfection, but Your commandment is without limit."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "97",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Oh, how I love Your law! All day long it is my meditation."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "98",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Your commandments make me wiser than my enemies, for they are always with me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "99",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I have more insight than all my teachers, for Your testimonies are my meditation."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "100",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I discern more than the elders, for I obey Your precepts."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "101",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I have kept my feet from every evil path, that I may keep Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "102",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I have not departed from Your ordinances, for You Yourself have taught me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "103",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "How sweet are Your words to my taste—sweeter than honey in my mouth!"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "104",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I gain understanding from Your precepts; therefore I hate every false way."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "105",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Your word is a lamp to my feet and a light to my path."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "106",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I have sworn and confirmedthat I will keep Your righteous judgments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "107",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I am severely afflicted, O LORD; revive me through Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "108",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Accept the freewill offerings of my mouth, O LORD, and teach me Your judgments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "109",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I constantly take my life in my hands, yet I do not forget Your law."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "110",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The wicked have set a snare for me, but I have not strayed from Your precepts."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "111",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Your testimonies are my heritage forever, for they are the joy of my heart."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "112",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I have inclined my heart to perform Your statutes, even to the very end."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "113",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The double-minded I despise, but Your law I love."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "114",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "You are my hiding place and my shield; I put my hope in Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "115",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Depart from me, you evildoers, that I may obey the commandments of my God."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "116",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Sustain me as You promised, that I may live; let me not be ashamed of my hope."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "117",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Uphold me, and I will be saved, that I may always regard Your statutes."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "118",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "You reject all who stray from Your statutes, for their deceitfulness is in vain."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "119",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "All the wicked on earth You discard like dross; therefore I love Your testimonies."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "120",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "My flesh trembles in awe of You; I st and in fear of Your judgments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "121",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I have done what is just and right; do not leave me to my oppressors."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "122",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Ensure Your servant’s well-being; do not let the arrogant oppress me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "123",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "My eyes fail, looking for Your salvation, and for Your righteous promise."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "124",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Deal with Your servant according to Your loving devotion, and teach me Your statutes."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "125",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I am Your servant; give me understanding, that I may know Your testimonies."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "126",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "It is time for the LORD to act, for they have broken Your law."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "127",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Therefore I love Your commandments more than gold, even the purest gold."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "128",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Therefore I admire all Your precepts and hate every false way."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "129",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Wonderful are Your testimonies; therefore I obey them."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "130",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The unfolding of Your words gives light; it informs the simple."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "131",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I open my mouth and pant, longing for Your commandments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "132",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Turn to me and show me mercy, as You do to those who love Your name."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "133",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Order my steps in Your word; let no sin rule over me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "134",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Redeem me from the oppression of man, that I may keep Your precepts."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "135",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Make Your face shine upon Your servant, and teach me Your statutes."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "136",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "My eyes shed streams of tearsbecause Your law is not obeyed."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "137",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Righteous are You, O LORD, and upright are Your judgments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "138",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The testimonies You have laid down are righteous and altogether faithful."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "139",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "My zeal has consumed mebecause my foes forget Your words."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "140",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Your promise is completely pure; therefore Your servant loves it."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "141",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I am lowly and despised, but I do not forget Your precepts."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "142",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Your righteousness is everlasting and Your law is true."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "143",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Trouble and distress have found me, but Your commandments are my delight."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "144",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Your testimonies are righteous forever. Give me understanding, that I may live."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "145",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I call with all my heart; answer me, O LORD! I will obey Your statutes."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "146",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I call to You; save me, that I may keep Your testimonies."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "147",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I rise before dawn and cry for help; in Your word I have put my hope."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "148",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "My eyes anticipate the watches of night, that I may meditate on Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "149",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Hear my voice, O LORD, according to Your loving devotion; give me life according to Your justice."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "150",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Those who follow after wickedness draw near; they are far from Your law."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "151",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "You are near, O LORD, and all Your commandments are true."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "152",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Long ago I learned from Your testimoniesthat You have established them forever."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "153",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Look upon my affliction and rescue me, for I have not forgotten Your law."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "154",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Defend my cause and redeem me; revive me according to Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "155",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Salvation is far from the wickedbecause they do not seek Your statutes."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "156",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Great are Your mercies, O LORD; revive me according to Your ordinances."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "157",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Though my persecutors and foes are many, I have not turned from Your testimonies."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "158",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I look on the faithless with loathingbecause they do not keep Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "159",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Consider how I love Your precepts, O LORD; give me life according to Your loving devotion."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "160",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The entirety of Your word is truth, and all Your righteous judgments endure forever."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "161",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Rulers persecute me without cause, but my heart fears only Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "162",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I rejoice in Your promiselike one who finds great spoil."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "163",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I hate and abhor falsehood, but Your law I love."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "164",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Seven times a day I praise Youfor Your righteous judgments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "165",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Abundant peace belongs to those who love Your instruction; nothing can make them stumble."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "166",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I wait for Your salvation, O LORD, and I carry out Your commandments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "167",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I obey Your testimonies and love them greatly."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "168",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I obey Your precepts and Your testimonies, for all my ways are before You."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "169",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "May my cry come before You, O LORD; give me understanding according to Your word."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "170",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "May my plea come before You; rescue me according to Your promise."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "171",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "My lips pour forth praise, for You teach me Your statutes."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "172",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "My tongue sings of Your word, for all Your commandments are righteous."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "173",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "May Your hand be ready to help me, for I have chosen Your precepts."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "174",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I long for Your salvation, O LORD, and Your law is my delight."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "175",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Let me live to praise You; may Your judgments sustain me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "176",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I have strayed like a lost sheep; seek Your servant, for I have not forgotten Your commandments."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    }
  ]
}